video.title: H2O: Just Add Water
video.synopsis: When three teens stranded on a remote island wander into a mystical pool during a full moon, they turn into mermaids with magical powers.

episodes.synopsis: Three teenage girls discover an underwater cavern on Mako Island and undergo a magical transformation.
episodes.title: Metamorphosis

episodes.synopsis: The girls are trying to keep their fish tails a secret, but when socialite Miriam throws a pool party, all they can do is try to stay dry.
episodes.title: Pool Party

episodes.synopsis: When the girls learn that sea turtles are getting caught in nets, it's Rikki and Emma to the rescue. But fishermen think they've got a shark problem.
episodes.title: Catch of the Day

episodes.synopsis: While deciding to throw her annual sleepover party, Emma heads to Mako Island in search of a clue.
episodes.title: Party Girls

episodes.synopsis: When Cleo's little sister gets ahold of Cleo's diary, she threatens to expose the three friends' secret.
episodes.title: Something Fishy

episodes.synopsis: Emma's younger brother, Elliot, develops a crush when he's saved from drowning.
episodes.title: Young Love

episodes.synopsis: A mysterious woman warns Cleo to steer clear of water and avoid looking at the full moon.
episodes.title: Moon Spell

episodes.synopsis: When Lewis takes a job as a research assistant to a noted marine biologist, the girls are worried that he might accidentally give away their secret.
episodes.title: The Denman Affair

episodes.synopsis: When Rikki tries to catch a fish for Cleo, she takes on a job offer from a breeder to collect rare fish that isn't what it seems.
episodes.title: Dangerous Waters

episodes.synopsis: The girls participate in a film contest but the heroic theme leaves the group at odds.
episodes.title: The Camera Never Lies

episodes.synopsis: A local surfing star asks Emma to be his swim coach but her secret makes her hesitant to dive into the role.
episodes.title: Sink or Swim

episodes.synopsis: As a full moon approaches, Cleo flexes her new pipes and sings a siren song that has the boys all over town swooning.
episodes.title: The Siren Effect

episodes.synopsis: Miss Chatham's mission to retrieve a precious piece of treasure lands her in a health emergency.
episodes.title: Shipwrecked

episodes.synopsis: Cleo faces yet another birthday party thrown by her dad. Zane is out to learn the identity of the sea creature he thinks saved his life.
episodes.title: Surprise!

episodes.synopsis: When Emma is put in charge of the caf√© for a weekend, her new employee Rikki has a tough time adjusting to her managerial style.
episodes.title: The Big Chill

episodes.synopsis: Zane continues the search for his sea savior. Meanwhile, Cleo's family and friends are convinced she has a secret boyfriend.
episodes.title: Lovesick

episodes.synopsis: On the day of a big biology exam, a thunderstorm has the girls faking sick to skip school.
episodes.title: Under the Weather

episodes.synopsis: Zane's investigation leads him to Mako Island, where he runs into a familiar face.
episodes.title: Bad Moon Rising

episodes.synopsis: When Cleo's cousin Angela comes to visit, she proves to be a wild child thirsty for fun in the water.
episodes.title: Hurricane Angela

episodes.synopsis: When Lewis enters a fishing contest, Cleo's plan to help him win backfires.
episodes.title: Hook, Line and Sinker

episodes.synopsis: Emma takes on a bold new hair color. Zane's sea monster mystery leads him to Miss Chatham and her old homestead.
episodes.title: Red Herring

episodes.synopsis: When Cleo and Emma find out about Rikki's new romance, Rikki must make a tough choice.
episodes.title: Fish Out of Water

episodes.synopsis: When Rikki spies a locket with an uncanny resemblance to Cleo's in a jewelry shop, Zane doesn't understand her desperate desire to possess it.
episodes.title: In Too Deep

episodes.synopsis: Emma and Cleo hope that Byron and Lewis will ask them to the school dance. Meanwhile, Lewis comes up with a special formula for the girls.
episodes.title: Love Potion #9

episodes.synopsis: Emma drops out of her family's annual vacation. Dr. Denman makes a discovery that brings her closer to the girls' secret.
episodes.title: Dr. Danger

episodes.synopsis: Cleo, Emma and Rikki must evade a trap set by Dr. Denman.
episodes.title: A Twist in the Tail

episodes.synopsis: Under the full moon, the girls undergo another transformation and must harness their newly enhanced powers.
episodes.title: Stormy Weather

episodes.synopsis: A new girl moves to the Gold Coast. Emma gives Elliott an assist on the soccer field. Cleo and Lewis' relationship takes a turn.
episodes.title: Control

episodes.synopsis: Zane tries to win Rikki back. Cleo tries to find dirt on Charlotte.
episodes.title: The One That Got Away

episodes.synopsis: Emma throws a wild house party. Nate offers to help Lewis with his hidden agenda.
episodes.title: Fire and Ice

episodes.synopsis: When Lewis uncovers an old book on mermaids, he and the girls test a potion recipe to surprising results.
episodes.title: Hocus Pocus

episodes.synopsis: Cleo is wary of the woman her dad invites over for dinner, especially when it turns out to be Charlotte's mother.
episodes.title: Pressure Cooker

episodes.synopsis: When Rikki and Emma try to help Cleo, they end up on a search for a missing dolphin at the Marine Park.
episodes.title: In Hot Water

episodes.synopsis: Zane gets tangled in a sticky situation while Rikki is forced to admit the truth about her background.
episodes.title: Wrong Side of the Tracks

episodes.synopsis: When a horse falls ill, Emma gets resourceful. Lewis looks for a date to an awards dinner.
episodes.title: Riding for a Fall

episodes.synopsis: When Cleo fails an exam, she is assigned to a new tutor. Meanwhile, her feelings for Lewis get complicated.
episodes.title: Missed the Boat

episodes.synopsis: A treasure hunt for a statue on the ocean floor with a hefty reward tests the girls' friendship.
episodes.title: In Over our Heads

episodes.synopsis: When Emma pricks her finger on a barb of coral, she starts to act more and more like a fish. Lewis tries to find a cure.
episodes.title: Fish Fever

episodes.synopsis: Don takes the family camping on Mako Island during a full moon -- leaving the girls to try and fight off its effects.
episodes.title: Moonwalker

episodes.synopsis: The juice bar Emma works at gets a new manager. A rivalry starts for Lewis' affection.
episodes.title: Get Off My Trail

episodes.synopsis: Lewis and Zane discover a scent that attracts mermaids. The girls start becoming drawn to Nate.
episodes.title: Irresistible

episodes.synopsis: Lewis is troubled by a dream about the mermaids being discovered. Meanwhile, Emma grows suspicious of Rikki and Ash's secret meetings.
episodes.title: Double Trouble

episodes.synopsis: Cleo and Rikki encourage Ash to make a bold romantic gesture for Emma -- but a full moon could thwart his plans.
episodes.title: Moonstruck

episodes.synopsis: When Zane and Ash clash, Rikki and Emma must choose sides. Cleo tries to organize a party celebrating the anniversary of their becoming mermaids.
episodes.title: The Heat is On

episodes.synopsis: Lewis tracks down a researcher to gain more insight into the girls' mermaid transformations.
episodes.title: The Gracie Code, Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The girls find an old reel of film from Max's research while Ash comes close to discovering Emma's secret.
episodes.title: The Gracie Code, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Charlotte looks into her grandmother's past and makes her way to the moon pool.
episodes.title: An Then There Were Four

episodes.synopsis: When the girls befriend a fourth mermaid, they bond as part of their school's beach volleyball team -- but Cleo, Emma and Rikki still have reservations.
episodes.title: Bubble Bubble Toil and Trouble

episodes.synopsis: The girls try to stop Charlotte, who begins to use her powers recklessly, to prevent their secret from being exposed.
episodes.title: Reckless

episodes.synopsis: Charlotte organizes a surprise party for Lewis. Cleo and Emma get trapped in a flooded storage room.
episodes.title: Three's Company

episodes.synopsis: When Charlotte meddles in Cleo and Lewis' friendship, Cleo runs away from home and gets caught in a dangerous situation.
episodes.title: Sea Change

episodes.synopsis: An opportunity to remove the girls' mermaid powers for good presents itself.
episodes.title: Unfathomable

episodes.synopsis: With their final year of high school ahead, Cleo and Rikki make a new friend in Bella, meet new boy Will and encounter a strange force on Mako Island.
episodes.title: The Awakening

episodes.synopsis: Will attempts to look into his experience on Mako Island, but Bella offers to direct him away from the moon pool to protect the girls' secret.
episodes.title: Jungle Hunt

episodes.synopsis: Cleo seeks a new job as an assistant dolphin trainer at the Marine Park. Meanwhile, Rikki takes issue with Nate's band playing at the cafe.
episodes.title: Keep Your Enemies Close

episodes.synopsis: The girls each are experiencing trouble in love as Cleo's father, Don, finds a pretty prospect.
episodes.title: Valentine's Day

episodes.synopsis: Zane hosts a dirt bike race to help the cafe bring in money. Lewis and Cleo continue with their moon pool investigation.
episodes.title: Big Ideas

episodes.synopsis: Bella sets up a study date with Will. Lewis pulls inspiration from the moon pool for his science project.
episodes.title: Secrets & Lies

episodes.synopsis: Cleo and Kim get to know their father's new girlfriend. Bella applies for a job at the cafe.
episodes.title: Happy Families

episodes.synopsis: Cleo hosts a sleepover for the girls on the night of the full moon -- until they end up on a rescue mission for Bella.
episodes.title: Kidnapped

episodes.synopsis: Cleo experiments with the magic moon pool water. Rikki later gets the water into Cleo's aquarium by accident.
episodes.title: The Sorcerer's Apprentice

episodes.synopsis: As Will begins to piece the mermaid mystery together, Bella tries to keep her secret from him.
episodes.title: Revealed

episodes.synopsis: When Bella helps Will with his diving, she tries to sort out his feelings for her. An unexpected booking has the cafe overrun with children.
episodes.title: Just a Girl at Heart

episodes.synopsis: When Rikki is held hostage, Will, Cleo and Bella must work together to save her.
episodes.title: Crime & Punishment

episodes.synopsis: Kim tries derailing Don and Samantha's wedding as Lewis receives an opportunity to study in America.
episodes.title: To Have & to Hold Back

episodes.synopsis: Will pushes himself too far when Zane challenges him to a free-diving competition. The girls discover a crystal in the rock from the moon pool.
episodes.title: Mermaid Magic

episodes.synopsis: Sophie swipes Bella's idea for a fundraising concert at the cafe.
episodes.title: Power Play

episodes.synopsis: Rikki goes to Mako Island to confront the strange force in the moon pool.
episodes.title: The Dark Side

episodes.synopsis: Cleo's introduced to Ryan, a young geophysicist working for Samantha. Rikki's time at the moon pool leads to a discovery about her powers.
episodes.title: A Magnetic Attraction

episodes.synopsis: Ryan sets out to explore Mako Island. To protect their secret, Rikki warns Bella and Cleo, and tries to stop Ryan from discovering the moon pool.
episodes.title: Into the Light

episodes.synopsis: Will competes in the free-diving championship competition and breaks away from Sophie's influence.
episodes.title: Breakaway

episodes.synopsis: Sophie lands a job at the cafe, to Bella's chagrin.
episodes.title: Queen for a Day

episodes.synopsis: The girls must recover a necklace containing a magic crystal when someone steals it to get Rikki's attention.
episodes.title: The Jewel Thief

episodes.synopsis: When the full moon rises early, the girls confront the water force and receive a message about Mako Island.
episodes.title: Mako Masters

episodes.synopsis: A massive beach party leaves room for misunderstandings -- until real feelings come to light.
episodes.title: Beach Party

episodes.synopsis: Cleo shows concern for her job when her father gets a second gig at the marine park.
episodes.title: Too Close for Comfort

episodes.synopsis: The girls must force a comet away from Earth using the magnetic crystals' powers.
episodes.title: A Date with Destiny

episodes.synopsis: The girls get resourceful to prevent the impact of the comet. Will they save Earth before graduation?
episodes.title: Graduation
